Title: Kemy Tamheomdae
Description: ['A season of ', Kemy, ', where the gang goes on expeditions to explore nature. This season is similar to the original ', Kemy Lang Buka Chaka, ' where some of the footage is live action nature. Still, Buka and Chaka do not reprise their roles in this season either.']
Related: ['Other: Kiki to Lala no Aoi Tori']
